a>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jordin-sparks-defends-chris-brown-amid-amas-controversy-people-deserve-to-be-able-to-grow-3355631">，乔丁·斯帕克斯 (Jordin Sparks) 与</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kelly-rowland">凯利·罗兰 (Kelly Rowland)</a>一起为布朗辩护。</p><p>在粉丝强烈反对后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joey-bada">乔伊·巴达$$</a>还为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joey-bada-defends-chris-brown-collaboration-after-backlash-from-fans-3280237">自己与布朗合作的决定进行了辩护</a>，称“人都会犯错误”。 2021 年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lizzo">利佐</a>因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-criticised-chris-brown-my-favourite-person-world-3060887">称这位歌手为“全世界他妈的我最喜欢的人”的</a>视频出现而在网上受到批评。</p><p>席亚拉<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ciara-attracts-backlash-for-new-collaboration-with-chris-brown-3478361">(Ciara) 因与克里斯·布朗 (Chris Brown) 的新合作而引起强烈反对的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
